INTENDED USE:
This software is designed specifically for students of Friedrich-Alexander-Universität
Erlangen-Nürnberg (FAU) to download their own course materials from StudOn
(studon.fau.de). The tool requires valid FAU authentication and only works with
the StudOn platform. Users are responsible for complying with FAU's terms of
service and using the tool responsibly.

While this license permits adaptation and modification, users at other institutions
should respect their own institution's policies and terms of service.

